testCancelContribution().notice: Tests successful cancellation of a contribution.

testCancelContributionFailsWhenEnded().notice: Tests that canceling a contribution fails when the campaign has ended.

testCancelContributionFailsWhenNoContrib.notice: Tests that canceling a contribution fails when there was no contribution.

testCancelContributionFailsWhenNotActive.notice: Tests that canceling a contribution fails when the campaign is not active.

testCancelContributionFailsWhenTransferF.notice: Tests that canceling a contribution fails if token transfer fails.

testContribute().notice: Tests successful contribution to a campaign.

testContributeFailsWhenCampaignEnded().notice: Tests that contributing to an ended campaign fails.

testContributeFailsWhenCampaignNotActive.notice: Tests that contributing to a non-active campaign fails.

testContributeFailsWhenCreatorContribute.notice: Tests that the campaign creator cannot contribute to their own campaign.

testContributeFailsWhenInvalidContributi.notice: Tests that contributing with an invalid amount (zero) fails.

testContributeFailsWhenTransferFailed().notice: Tests that a contribution fails if token transfer fails.

testCreateCampaignFailsWhenAmountZero().notice: Tests that creating a campaign with zero amount fails.

testCreateCampaignFailsWhenShortDuration.notice: Tests that creating a campaign with a duration of zero days fails.

testGetCampaignFailsWhenInvalidCampaignI.notice: Tests the `getCampaign` function with an invalid campaign ID.

testGetCampaignReturnsDefaultValuesWhenC.notice: Tests that `getCampaign` returns default values when the campaign does not exist.

testGetContributionFailsWhenNoContributi.notice: Tests that `getContribution` returns zero if there was no contribution.

testRefundFailsWhenCampaignNotEnded().notice: Tests that refunding fails when the campaign has not ended.

testRefundFailsWhenGoalReached().notice: Tests that refunding fails when the campaign goal was reached.

testRefundFailsWhenNoContributionToRefun.notice: Tests that refunding fails when there are no contributions to refund.

testRefundFundsFailsTransferFailed().notice: Tests that refunding funds fails if token transfer fails.

testWithdrawFunds().notice: Tests successful withdrawal of funds by the campaign creator.

testWithdrawFundsFailsWhenCampaignNotEnd.notice: Tests that withdrawing funds fails if the campaign has not ended.

testWithdrawFundsFailsWhenGoalNotReached.notice: Tests that withdrawing funds fails if the campaign goal was not reached.

testWithdrawFundsFailsWhenNotCampaignCre.notice: Tests that a non-campaign creator cannot withdraw funds.

testWithdrawFundsFailsWhenTransferFailed.notice: Tests that withdrawing funds fails if token transfer fails.
